text: Einar Hermann (10 August 1878 - 7 September 1953) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1878 births Category:1953 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
